</head>

<body>
	<div id="mood">
	</div>

	<div id="question" class="">
		<a href="#" class="js-open-modal">?</a>
	</div>

	<div id="modal" class="">
		NOTE: As of 3/7/2018, the WorldWideWeather Premium API has expired. To see screenshots of this website's features, please visit the <a href="https://github.com/aleesteele/global-cities">Github guide</a>.<br/><br/>
